<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Админ Панел</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styling */
        body {
            background-image: url('../images/pngtree-technology-round-dashboard-image_908915.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed; /* Keeps the background static */
            color: #ecf0f1; /* Text in light grey for contrast */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Admin Panel Container */
        .admin-panel {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

            .admin-panel h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                color: #00FFFF;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
                animation: bounceIn 1.5s ease-out;
            }

            /* Button Styling */
            .admin-panel .menu {
                display: flex;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                gap: 20px;
                justify-content: center;
            }

                .admin-panel .menu a {
                    text-decoration: none;
                    background-color: #3498db;
                    color: white;
                    font-size: 1.2rem;
                    font-weight: bold;
                    padding: 15px 30px;
                    border-radius: 5px;
                    box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                    transition: transform 0.3s ease, background-color 0.3s ease;
                }

                    .admin-panel .menu a:hover {
                        background-color: #1abc9c;
                        transform: scale(1.1);
                    }

        /* Keyframe Animations */
        @@keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        @@keyframes bounceIn {
            0% {
                transform: scale(0.8);
                opacity: 0;
            }

            60% {
                transform: scale(1.1);
                opacity: 1;
            }

            100% {
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="admin-panel">
        <h1>Админ Панел</h1>
        <div class="menu">
            <a href="/Admin/ManageUsers">Управление на потребители</a>
            <a href="/AdminReservation/Manage">Управление на резервации</a>
            <a href="/AdminPromotion">Управление на промоции</a>
            <a href="/AdminLocation">Управление на локации</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
